content: A photo from a walk on 2025-03-16.

photos.alt: A photo of a leafless oak tree. It is in the center of the frame, with many branches filling the rest, black and brown against the cloudy grey and blue sky. A bit of sunlight can be visible on its trunk and branches, and the bottom of the trunk is covered in green vines. A few other trees can be visible around: one oak further away, and a few branches of other trees visible on the edges of the frame.
